text: Mario Abdo Benítez (born 10 November 1971) is a Paraguayan politician. He served as president of the Senate of Paraguay. Abdo Benítez is the 51st President of Paraguay from 15 August 2018 to 15 August 2023. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official campaign website *Biography by CIDOB (in Spanish) Category:Living people Category:1971 births Category:Presidents of Paraguay Category:Current national leaders Category:People from Asunción
